## Key Findings

**CRITICAL**: OAuth state verification is **correctly implemented** with httpOnly cookies (lines 52-60 in `app/api/auth/myob/callback/route.ts`). Verifies CSRF before token exchange. ✅

**WARNING**: Gemini batch processor (lib/ai/batch-processor.ts) uses hardcoded 15 req/min limit but Vercel instances are stateless — rate limiting is **not shared across parallel functions**. Should use Upstash Redis for distributed enforcement.

**DEBT**: Amendment period calculation duplicated across all 16 analysis engines. Refactor to `lib/utils/amendment-period.ts` utility function.

**COMPLIANCE**: All Xero operations READ-ONLY (no token can modify). Encryption at rest (AES-256-GCM). Multi-tenant isolation via RLS on 9 tables. ✅